column2: "...let's talk. Did that happen right after I came back here?..."
"After defeating a dragon, went in high spirits to give a report to the intel team sisters, meow."
"But, listen to this! The twins were there vigorously saying, \"that dragon sure was tough\"!"
"Professor...I want to become a strong cat that everyone can really rely on, meow."
"So I'd be happy if you'd take me along on missions more in the future, meow. Until then, meow!"
